resources.string: Try for 1 minute to make the maximum number of push-ups (chest), rest 30 seconds and do the maximum number of squats (legs) in 2 minutes, rest 45 seconds and do the maximum amount of sit-ups (press) for 3 minutes. Do not embellish your results, if you start with the wrong level, it is possible to significantly reduce the effectiveness of the training. Even if your initial result will be more than modest, do not worry, you can achieve maximum success, if you are honest with ourselves, from the beginning to the end of the training.

Triple Impact - is a simple but very effective 6-weeks fat-burning training plan. You will be doing push-ups, immediately turning to squatting, and then immediately to the sit-ups(press). It is important to keep the proper technique while performing all exercises. Before you start the workouts, you need to consult with a doctor and perform an initial test on the basis of which your actual level of training will be defined. Workouts should be conducted three times a week, between workouts has to be at least one day of rest.
